plot: Dee discovers that the biggest loser and fatty from high school is now a successful and thin fashion designer... now making Dee the biggest loser.

Dee discovers that her old high school friend "Fatty McGoo," the only girl in school who was a bigger loser than she was, is now a successful fashion designer. She and Dennis compete to create dress designs while Frank and Mac open a sweatshop to manufacture Dennis' dresses.—Bruno Antony
